10.6 using yum groups

yum groups are provided to give access to specific categories of software. 

yum groups list will list the most common yum groups.

yum groups list hidden shows all yum groups

yum groups info <groupname> will give more info on a yum groupname

yum groups install <groupname> will install a yum group

use yum groups install --with-optional <groupname> to install everything

yum groups are similar to modules, but more focused on running services. They will provide everything needed to run various services. 